      <title>Hexo 前言</title>
      <link href="2021/04/10/2021-04-10-hexo-intro/"/>
      <url>2021/04/10/2021-04-10-hexo-intro/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo 是一個透過指令生成的靜態網頁，主要採用 Markdown 格式編寫文章。因為純靜態的特性，所以可以架設在如 Github 之類的免費平台，透過指令操作與支援 .md 文章，與工程師的使用習慣相符，所以吸引許多人使用。</p><p>我習慣使用 Notion 做學習筆記，所以學習架設 Hexo ，並將我的筆記經過彙編，發表為部落格文章。透過整理學習心得的過程，強化自己學到的知識，也分享自己的經驗給更多人。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Hexo </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Create a new vue cli</title>
      <link href="2021/04/10/2021-04-10-Create-a-new-vue-cli/"/>
      <url>2021/04/10/2021-04-10-Create-a-new-vue-cli/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安裝-Vue-Cli"><a href="#安裝-Vue-Cli" class="headerlink" title="安裝 Vue Cli"></a>安裝 Vue Cli</h1><p>課程是以 vue-cli 2 的版本，如果是這個版本，可以執行以下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vue init webpack &lt;project name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span><p>如果你跟我一樣裝了 vue cli3 ，可以使用 vue create &lt;專案名&gt;，安裝時可選擇 vue 2 版本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vue create &lt;project name&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 執行</span><br><span class="line">npm run serve</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>註：<code>npm run dev</code> 跟 <code>npm run serve</code> 只是在 package.json 裡的名稱不同而已</p><h1 id="安裝-Bootstrap-node-sass-sass-loader"><a href="#安裝-Bootstrap-node-sass-sass-loader" class="headerlink" title="安裝 Bootstrap node-sass sass-loader"></a>安裝 Bootstrap node-sass sass-loader</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install bootstrap node-sass sass-loader --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>測試 scss 有沒有裝好</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><figcaption><span>app.vue</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style lang=<span class="string">&quot;scss&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  $color: black;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  body &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    background-color: $color;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>style裡改用 @import 方式引入 BS，放入 BS HTML 元件看效果</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;div id=<span class="string">&quot;app&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- 要顯示的內容一定要放在 #app 裡面 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div id=<span class="string">&quot;nav&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;router-link to=<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>&gt;Home&lt;/router-link&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      |</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;router-link to=<span class="string">&quot;/about&quot;</span>&gt;About&lt;/router-link&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;router-view/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card&quot;</span> style=<span class="string">&quot;width: 18rem;&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card-body&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;h5 <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card-title&quot;</span>&gt;Card title&lt;/h5&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;p <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card-text&quot;</span>&gt;Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk <span class="keyword">of</span> the card<span class="string">&#x27;s</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          content.&lt;/p&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-primary&quot;&gt;Go somewhere&lt;/a&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">      &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;!-- 要顯示的內容一定要放在 #app 裡面 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">  &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;/template&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;style lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">@import &quot;~bootstrap/scss/bootstrap&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在 HelloWorld.vue 上有 scoped 限制樣式只能在該元件上</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style scoped lang=<span class="string">&quot;scss&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="install-axios"><a href="#install-axios" class="headerlink" title="install axios"></a>install axios</h1><p>url: <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/vue-axios">https://www.npmjs.com/package/vue-axios</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install --save axios vue-axios</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>at main.js import</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><figcaption><span>main.js</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> axios <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;axios&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> VueAxios <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;vue-axios&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// use</span></span><br><span class="line">Vue.use(VueAxios, axios)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果你不小心安裝了 es-lint ，運行時出現提示應修正錯誤，可以用以下指令查找主要錯誤的地方。</p><p>顯示主要錯誤（忽略prettier）</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm run lint --fix</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-shop@<span class="number">0.1</span><span class="number">.0</span> lint</span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-cli-service lint</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">error: <span class="string">&#x27;HelloWorld&#x27;</span> is defined but never used (no-unused-vars) at src/App.vue:<span class="number">29</span>:<span class="number">8</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">27</span> |</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">28</span> | &lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; <span class="number">29</span> | <span class="keyword">import</span> HelloWorld <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./components/HelloWorld&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     |        ^</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">30</span> |</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">31</span> | <span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">32</span> |   name: <span class="string">&quot;App&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span> error found.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果修正錯誤後沒有問題，則會出現…</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm run lint --fix</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-shop@<span class="number">0.1</span><span class="number">.0</span> lint</span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-cli-service lint</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> DONE  No lint errors found!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用 axios</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  name: <span class="string">&quot;App&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">created</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span> &#123;    <span class="comment">// 我不小心打成 create() 測試半天才找到原因</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.$http.get(<span class="string">&quot;https://randomuser.me/api/&quot;</span>).then(<span class="function">(<span class="params">response</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(response);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="增加自訂-API-路徑"><a href="#增加自訂-API-路徑" class="headerlink" title="增加自訂 API 路徑"></a>增加自訂 API 路徑</h1><p>就是我們申請的自訂 API 路徑。課程說要修改 config\ 目錄下的設定檔，增加 API 常數，但使用新版本 Vue Cli3 在根目錄中已經沒有 config 、build 等目錄，如果要加常數，要在「根目錄」加入「.env」檔案，內容為：</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">常數名稱=value</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>常數一定要以 VUE_APP_ 為前置命名，例如：</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">VUE_APP_&#123;variable name&#125;=value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">example:</span><br><span class="line">VUE_APP_APIPATH=https:<span class="comment">//vue-course-api.herokuapp.com</span></span><br><span class="line">VUE_APP_CUSTOMPATH=joe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>改完要重新運行服務才會生效。據網上資料，如果輸出常數得到 undefined ，可能原因有三種：</p><ol><li><p>.env 沒在根目錄，如在 /src</p></li><li><p>要以 VUE_APP_ 開頭，如果沒有，也會出現 undefined</p></li><li><p>改完要重啟服務 npm run serve</p></li></ol><h1 id="組合-api-路徑，測試是否正常"><a href="#組合-api-路徑，測試是否正常" class="headerlink" title="組合 api 路徑，測試是否正常"></a>組合 api 路徑，測試是否正常</h1><figure class="highlight jsx"><figcaption><span>app.vue</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">created</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> api = <span class="string">`<span class="subst">$&#123;process.env.VUE_APP_APIPATH&#125;</span>/api/<span class="subst">$&#123;process.env.VUE_APP_CUSTOMPATH&#125;</span>/products`</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.$http.get(api)</span><br><span class="line">      .then(<span class="function">(<span class="params">response</span>) =&gt;</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(response)</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>得到結果：<br><img src="01.png" alt="alt"></p><h1 id="🌍-Resources"><a href="#🌍-Resources" class="headerlink" title="🌍  Resources"></a>🌍  Resources</h1><p>|D2| Vue CLI3 安裝與建立 vue 專案 - iT 邦幫忙::一起幫忙解決難題，拯救 IT 人的一天<br><a href="https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/articles/10216606">https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/articles/10216606</a></p><p>解讀 vue-cli 腳手架（一）：npm run dev的背後 - IT閱讀<br><a href="https://www.itread01.com/content/1550372949.html">https://www.itread01.com/content/1550372949.html</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
